The paper discusses models of quantum computation and quantum programming languages, which are topics related to computer science theory (cs.THE), quantum information (cs.QI), and programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also mentions the use of formal methods (cs.LO) and complexity theory (cs.CC) in the context of quantum computing. However, since the focus of the paper is on quantum computing and programming languages, cs.ET (Emerging Technologies) is the most likely sub-category.
